swapEtherToToken(address,uint256).details: makes a trade from Ether to token. Sends token to msg sender

params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade is canceled.

swapTokenToEther(address,uint256,uint256.details: makes a trade from token to Ether, sends Ether to msg sender

params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade is canceled.

swapTokenToToken(address,uint256,address.details: makes a trade between src and dest token and send dest tokens to msg sender

params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade is canceled.

trade(address,uint256,address,address,ui.details: makes a trade between src and dest token and send dest token to destAddress

params.maxDestAmount: A limit on the amount of dest tokens
params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade is canceled.
params.walletId: is the wallet ID to send part of the fees

tradeWithHint(address,uint256,address,ad.details: makes a trade between src and dest token and send dest token to destAddress

params.hint: will give hints for the trade.
params.maxDestAmount: A limit on the amount of dest tokens
params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade is canceled.
params.walletId: is the wallet ID to send part of the fees
